column2: I'm signing this much needed petition because abuse doesn't need to be violent in order to cause pain or hurt. Yes, women do abuse men, no matter their size. The mind is  very powerful and sometimes mental abuse is worse than physical abuse  I recognized this in Amber Heard the minute she opened her mouth. If you have ever experienced it yourself, then PLEASE use you're voice and let's support this awesome and humble man and sign!  NEVER let ANYONE make you feel less than you deserve!!! #justiceforjohnnydepp #justicefordepp
